summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting an easement over portions of Blocks 139, 146 and 147; and over vacated streets therein; over a portion of Larmie St. (as vacated in Ordinance 5012); and over a portion of Puget Ave. W. (as vacated in Ordinance 5011), all in Seattle Tidelands; also, accepting a deed to a portion of Block 147 of Seattle Tidelands for pedestrian and bicycle purposes.
